dct_title_s: Map of Melbourne and its vicinity
dct_description_sm: Legend indicates tram and rail ways "shewn thus."
Detached from The Melbourne Guide Book, illustrated by bird's-eye views of the streets, pictorial map of the city... (original cataloger's note).
Also shows city plan, parks, waterways, vegetation, numerous facilities including Melbourne Cemetery and Metropolitan Lunatic Asylum, with illustrations.
